  • Method Details

    • insert

      public void insert(String word)
      Saves first letter of string. Checks if said letter is in the node's hashmap. If not, make a new node and save it in the hashmap, with the letter as the key. If yes, and if the word is not 1 character long, recursively call this method for the child. If it is 1 character long, Set "isWord" to true.
      Parameters:
      word - string to insert into a node
